{/* merchand */}

Become A Ground Owner

Maidan is the Pakistans top search and booking site for recreational sports.
{/* row */}

Owner benefits:

Here are some interesting benefits for merchant Meidan App to enjoy business growth exponentially. No other platform can provide such amazing benefits.{" "}

{/* Row */}
{/* Column */}
Easily manageable:

The Meidan app is easily manageable for sports ground listing from anywhere anytime. It can even work in other countries as well. You would just need an internet connection to manage it.


{/* Column */}
Eliminate book keeping system

Maintaining journals is the old way of keeping records. It takes time, energy, and labor. After all the efforts, it can be destroyed and replaced so easily. Registration form for Meidan merchants are available online.


{/* Column */}
More users than regular old system

As we all know people have shifted to internet and online search for desire problem. Like other developed countries, Meidan has also decided to make things easier than before for Pakistanis.


{/* Column */}
More profit

Meidan is solving the hurdle to track customers and book appointments by sports ground listing. It enhances the business and removes the problems of access. This will automatically generate more customers and end up with a larger amount of profit.

{/* Column */}
Referral download reward RS 50

Merchant will reward RS 50 to his Meidan Wallet, only if he refers any user to sports ground listing through the Meidan App. And the one who is a referral will reward RS 50 to the Meidan Wallet.


{/* Column */}
Merchant has Peak hours selection power

Peak hour is amazing feature of the Meidan App. Merchant has its own power to select peak hours to earn more profit. There isnt any restriction from Company as there is no power limit to earn.


{/* Column */}
No freemium, only premium even more premium than usual{" "}

No merchant is liable to give freemium to any customer. Merchant is independent for choosing charges from the ground user.{" "}

{/* Column */}
Cancelation profit to merchant

Whenever a user cancels its booking of ground, the merchant will charge him particular amount. As the cancelation chart is already maintained.


{/* Column */}
Easy to use and healthy income

Its not difficult to use and manage. Even it clears all the barrier of booking grounds. Merchant can earn ten times more than usual income.


{/* steps */}

Steps to join merchant Meidan App

Registration as a user:

STEP 1

First of all, like any common user needs to register Meidan account.

{/* 2 */}

Settings to become Merchant:

STEP 2

The user has to Go to Account settings and then click "to become a merchant" option.
There will be a KYC form. Fill in all the requirements and submit it to become a merchant on Meidan.

{/* 3 */}

Verification Email:

STEP 3

Within 24 hours KYC form is analyzed and reviewed to check accuracy of filled information. Meidan accepts the form after satisfying all the mentioned details.
Rejection/acceptance email will be delivered to the applicant.

{/* 4 */}

Manual Merchant App:

STEP 4

Meidan team hand over merchant app manually. That mean team itself will deliver you App to use merchant account accordingly

{/* 5 */}

Download Merchant App:

STEP 5

It is also possible to download merchant app from Meidan website. Merchant can download it from website. Manual installation is recommended in case of any mismanagement.

{/* 6 */}

Log in Merchant App

STEP 6

Merchant needs to log in after attaining manual App.

{/* 7 */}

Manage merchant App:

STEP 7

Merchants can manage App with attractive images of grounds, players and tournaments. Publish "Time slots" and "charges" schedules.

{/* hero */}
); } } export default Merchant;
